 *   /sys/block/loop0/   (directory)   .. loop7
 *   /sys/block/loopX/dev   (file)     "7:N\n"
 *   /sys/block/loopX/size  (file)     "0\n" (placeholder)
 *   /sys/block/loopX/uevent (file)    empty
